x4freetext: The integrated bombardment current was measured by the
activity of 65Zn in 18 mg/cm 2 copper monitor foils.
Samples of erbium oxide Er2O3 (conversion ratio of
yield to pure erbium 1.28)
The uncertainties of the Tm-165,Tm-166,Tm-167,
Tm-168 yields include systematic error of nuclide
activity measurement and error of integral current
measurement (11-12%). The uncertainties of the Tm-170
yield determine by exception procedure of 79.82 keV
Tu-168 gamma-line background in 84.26 keV Tu-170 gamma-
line photopeak (18-20%).
